<div id="section1"><h2>Who Are We?</h2><p>Established in 1993 in the steel city of Sheffield, we originally formed to satisfy a niche as a "specialist stockholder" for commercial hot rolled strip.  Customer demand and our reputation for being able to source more unusual specifications and technical products has enhanced our range to include cold rolled strip, stainless strip and flat bar amongst many.</p>
</div>
    
