<div id="section5"><h2>A Wealth of Experience</h2><p>Our team includes fully qualified metallurgists with a combined 70 years experience within the steel industry.  Such expertise enables technical liaison and product back-up at the customers works, and our knowledge has earned us a reputation for being able to source material when all else fails.</p></div>
 
<div id="section2">
      <div id="slideshow2">
      <img src="Images/hot rolled coils 2.jpg" width="350" height="210" alt="slit narrow coil"/>
