      </div>
</div>   
       
<div id="section6"><h2>Independent Stockists</h2><p>Over time we have developed close working relationships with several European mills and processors, however crucially we remain independent.  As such we are best equipped to source from the most beneficial supply route for the customer and we are free to locate those 'difficult to find’ products.</p>
</div>
 
